OL,5, The owner of HMV is edging closer to a 
OL,6, deal to buy collapsed discounter Wilko,
OL,7, saving thousands of jobs and the       
OL,8, majority of shops, the BBC understands.
OL,10,FDoug Putman plans to keep up to 300 of 
OL,11,Fthe current 400 Wilko shops open if he 
OL,12,Fsucceeds in buying the chain.          
OL,14,FIf the deal goes ahead, it would mean  
OL,15,Fthousands of the current 12,500 jobs at
OL,16,Frisk could be saved.                   
OL,18,FThe development comes after a bid from 
OL,19,Fprivate equity firm M2 Capital to buy  
OL,20,Fthe business fell through.             
